Define a function which can compute the sum of two numbers using recursion.

sample input:

4

8

Sample output:

12

import java.util.*;
public class sotn
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
        int a=sc.nextInt();
        int b=sc.nextInt();
        if(b==0)
        {
            System.out.print(a);
        }
        else
        {
            System.out.print(a+b);
        }
    }
}
